lt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FzH1X10Bc6M/UkrZ0_oYZfI/AAAAAAAAo9M/njHQ39TrHSA/s1600/IMG_20131001_104214_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FzH1X10Bc6M/UkrZ0_oYZfI/AAAAAAAAo9M/njHQ39TrHSA/s320/IMG_20131001_104214_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&amp;id=2ea93c5b7b\" method=\"POST\"><a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a></p>\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[13386,16910,27418]}